OL,5, A black police officer in the US state 
OL,6, of Ohio has filed a discrimination     
OL,7, complaint after allegedly receiving a  
OL,8, racist note from a superior officer.   
OL,10,FOfficer Keith Pool made the complaint  
OL,11,Fafter video footage emerged of         
OL,12,Fthen-Sheffield Lake Police Chief       
OL,13,FAnthony Campo placing a note on his    
OL,14,Fdesk reading "Ku Klux Klan" (KKK) last 
OL,15,FJune.                                  
OL,17,FIt is also alleged Mr Campo engaged in 
OL,18,Fongoing racist abuse against Mr Pool.  
OL,20,FMr Campo has since resigned and said   
OL,21,Fhis actions were "a joke".             
